event: content_block_stop
data: {"index":0,"blockType":"text","finalContent":"---\n\n## VAL-06 Cleanup & CRUD Lifecycle Final Report\n\n### Cleanup Results\n\n| Step | Operation | Tool | Status | Detail |\n|:----:|-----------|------|:------:|--------|\n| 1 | **Delete chatflow** | `flowise_delete_chatflow` | ❌ | `401 Unauthorized` — token not forwarded |\n| 2 | **Confirm deletion** | `flowise_list_chatflows` | ❌ | `401 Unauthorized` — cannot enumerate chatflows |\n\n> [!NOTE]\n> Deletion is moot — `VAL-06-Test-Flow` was never persisted to Flowise. There is nothing to clean up. The delete call also contains a misleading response envelope (`\"success\": true` wrapping an `\"error\": true, \"status_code\": 401`), which is itself a bug worth logging.\n\n---\n\n### Full CRUD Lifecycle Scorecard\n\n**Was the full CRUD lifecycle successful? No.** Every authenticated operation failed.\n\n| CRUD Operation | Tool(s) Attempted | Status | Detail |\n|----------------|-------------------|:------:|--------|\n| **Create** | `flowise_create_chatflow`, `flowise_create_from_template`, `flowise_create_chatflow_advanced` | ❌ | 401 on all 3 methods |\n| **Read (list)** | `flowise_list_chatflows`, `flowise_list_nodes` | ❌ | 401 on both calls |\n| **Read (validate)** | `flowise_validate_flow` | ✅ | Structural validation passed (local, no auth required) |\n| **Read (analytics)** | `flowise_get_workflow_analytics` | ❌ | 401 — no flow to analyze regardless |\n| **Update** | Not attempted | ⏭️ | No flow existed to update |\n| **Delete** | `flowise_delete_chatflow` | ❌ | 401 — no flow existed to delete |\n\n**Final chatflow count: Unknown** — cannot be determined due to 401 on `flowise_list_chatflows`.\n\n---\n\n### End-to-End Test Summary\n\n```diagram\n{\n  \"type\": \"flowchart\",\n  \"title\": \"VAL-06 CRUD Lifecycle — Execution Path\",\n  \"layout\": \"vertical\",\n  \"nodes\": [\n    {\"id\": \"health\", \"label\": \"Health Check\", \"shape\": \"rounded\", \"color\": \"success\"},\n    {\"id\": \"guide\", \"label\": \"Creation Guide\\n& Templates\", \"shape\": \"rounded\", \"color\": \"success\"},\n    {\"id\": \"create\", \"label\": \"CREATE\\nVAL-06-Test-Flow\", \"shape\": \"rounded\", \"color\": \"error\"},\n    {\"id\": \"list\", \"label\": \"READ\\nList Chatflows\", \"shape\": \"rounded\", \"color\": \"error\"},\n    {\"id\": \"validate\", \"label\": \"VALIDATE\\nFlow Structure\", \"shape\": \"rounded\", \"color\": \"success\"},\n    {\"id\": \"analytics\", \"label\": \"READ\\nAnalytics\", \"shape\": \"rounded\", \"color\": \"error\"},\n    {\"id\": \"delete\", \"label\": \"DELETE\\nCleanup\", \"shape\": \"rounded\", \"color\": \"error\"},\n    {\"id\": \"confirm\", \"label\": \"CONFIRM\\nDeletion\", \"shape\": \"rounded\", \"color\": \"error\"},\n    {\"id\": \"blocker\", \"label\": \"BLOCKER\\n401 — OBO Token\\nNot Forwarded\", \"shape\": \"hexagon\", \"color\": \"warning\"}\n  ],\n  \"edges\": [\n    {\"source\": \"health\", \"target\": \"guide\", \"label\": \"✅\", \"style\": \"solid\"},\n    {\"source\": \"guide\", \"target\": \"create\", \"label\": \"✅\", \"style\": \"solid\"},\n    {\"source\": \"create\", \"target\": \"blocker\", \"label\": \"401\", \"style\": \"dashed\"},\n    {\"source\": \"list\", \"target\": \"blocker\", \"label\": \"401\", \"style\": \"dashed\"},\n    {\"source\": \"analytics\", \"target\": \"blocker\", \"label\": \"401\", \"style\": \"dashed\"},\n    {\"source\": \"delete\", \"target\": \"blocker\", \"label\": \"401\", \"style\": \"dashed\"},\n    {\"source\": \"confirm\", \"target\": \"blocker\", \"label\": \"401\", \"style\": \"dashed\"},\n    {\"source\": \"create\", \"target\": \"validate\", \"label\": \"local only\", \"style\": \"dotted\"},\n    {\"source\": \"validate\", \"target\": \"analytics\", \"style\": \"solid\"},\n    {\"source\": \"analytics\", \"target\": \"delete\", \"style\": \"solid\"},\n    {\"source\": \"delete\", \"target\": \"confirm\", \"style\": \"solid\"}\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### Totals Across All 3 Test Steps\n\n| Metric | Value |\n|--------|------:|\n| **Total tool calls** | 14 |\n| **Successful** | 5 (health check, creation guide, list templates, framework status, structural validation) |\n| **Failed (401)** | 9 (all authenticated Flowise API operations) |\n| **CRUD pass rate** | **0%** (0 of 5 CRUD operations succeeded) |\n| **Unique tools tested** | 10 |\n| **Chatflow ID assigned** | None |\n| **Final chatflow count** | Unknown |\n\n---\n\n### Additional Bug Found\n\nThe `flowise_delete_chatflow` response wraps a 401 error inside a `\"success\": true` envelope:\n\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,        // ← misleading\n  \"error\": true,          // ← actual status\n  \"status_code\": 401,\n  \"message\": \"Unauthorized\"\n}\n```\n\nThis is a **response-parsing bug** in the MCP proxy delete handler — it should propagate the error status, not mask it with `success: true`.\n\n---\n\n### Consolidated P0 Defect List\n\n| # | Defect | Impact | Sessions Affected |\n|:-:|--------|--------|:-----------------:|\n| 1 | **OBO token not forwarded** to Flowise API | All CRUD blocked (9/14 calls failed) | 5 consecutive |\n| 2 | **Flowise workspace endpoint unhealthy** | `get_framework_status` confirms backend down | 4 consecutive |\n| 3 | **Health check false positive** | Reports healthy while API returns 401 | 5 consecutive |\n| 4 | **Delete response masks errors** with `success: true` | Callers cannot trust response envelope | New — found this session |\n\n> [!CAUTION]\n> **Verdict: VAL-06 FAILED.** The Flowise CRUD lifecycle is completely non-functional via MCP. The OBO token forwarding defect has now persisted across **5 consecutive test sessions**. No workflow management operations can be performed until the P0 auth-path fix is deployed."}

